1. Juče smo *postavili* novi tepih u dnevnoj sobi. (Yesterday, we *placed* a new carpet in the living room.)
2. Radnici su već *postavili* temelje za novu zgradu. (The workers have already *laid* the foundations for the new building.)
3. Kada smo *postavili* pitanje, niko nije imao odgovor. (When we *posed* the question, nobody had an answer.)
4. Predsednik je *postavio* novog ministra u vladi. (The president *appointed* a new minister in the government.)
5. Svi gosti su već *postavili* tanjire na stol. (All the guests have already *placed* plates on the table.)
6. Naša firma je nedavno *postavila* novi rekord u prodaji. (Our company recently *set* a new sales record.)
7. Ovaj projekat zahteva da se *postave* nove ciljeve. (This project requires *establishing* new goals.)
8. Majstor je upravo *postavio* novi zid u kuhinji. (The handyman has just *erected* a new wall in the kitchen.)
9. Mlada mama je *postavila* bebu u kolica. (The young mother *put* the baby in the stroller.)
10. Sutra ćemo *postaviti* novi oglas za posao. (Tomorrow we will *post* a new job ad.)